{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_01PhwF6EwVGUrJFHrYPdmbKV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The booking is complete. Now for STEP 4: I need to provide a final summary to the user with all the information.","signature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**STEP 4: BOOKING COMPLETE ✓**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Booking Summary\n\n**Confirmation Code:** ABC123XYZ\n\n### Flight Details\n- **Flight:** AF1234 - Air France\n- **Route:** New York (JFK) → Paris (CDG)\n- **Date:** June 15, 2024\n- **Departure:** 09:00 (JFK)\n- **Arrival:** 22:30 (CDG)\n- **Class:** Economy\n- **Seat:** 12A (Window)\n\n### Passenger Information\n- **Name:** John Smith\n- **Email:** john.smith@example.com\n- **Total Price:** €350\n\n### Destination Information (Paris)\n- **Current Weather:** Sunny, 18°C, humidity 65%, light breeze from west\n- **Local Time:** 14:30 CET (UTC+1)\n\n---\n\n✉️ A confirmation email has been sent to john.smith@example.com with your e-ticket and booking details. Have a great flight to Paris! 🛫"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":13,"cache_creation_input_tokens":291,"cache_read_input_tokens":2211,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":291,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":292,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}}